Definition: to an extreme degree
Example: extremely cold; extremely unpleasant; she is super smart; the night was deathly cold; as a child, I was deathly afraid of snakes
Synonyms: adj, all, intense, extreme, exceedingly, super, deathly, to, an, degree, cold, unpleasant, she, is, smart, the, night, was, as, a, child, I, afraid, of, snakes
Category: adv.all
